 703:Drivers/CMSIS/Include/cmsis_gcc.h ****   \param [in]  value  Value to be saturated
 704:Drivers/CMSIS/Include/cmsis_gcc.h ****   \param [in]    sat  Bit position to saturate to (1..32)
