1751:Drivers/CMSIS/Include/core_cm7.h ****   \brief   Mask and shift a bit field value for use in a register bit range.
1752:Drivers/CMSIS/Include/core_cm7.h ****   \param[in] field  Name of the register bit field.
1753:Drivers/CMSIS/Include/core_cm7.h ****   \param[in] value  Value of the bit field. This parameter is interpreted as an uint32_t type.
